fields.title: Software Developer
fields.bio: Hello, my name is Danang Haris Setiawan and I am a student at UDINUS majoring in Computer Science. I am a full-stack software developer with no experience working other than remote work in the past three years as a Software Engineer and Data Analytics. Apart from programming, I have great interests in martial arts, writing, and music

fields.title: Darisset Blog with Django
fields.abstract:
This project is named Darisset, so if you are using this Project to create your own project, you will need a little extra configuration. As:
1. Darisset.site folder (your top project container)
2. Darisset_site/darisset folder (your project name)
3. Virtual environment name: env (name whatever you want)
4. Create in the virtual environment an .env file
5. You must change from set.settings.development to your projectname.settings.development.
6. The same work for the test env
fields.content:
With this code, you can create complex Django-based websites. very fast, just a few steps!

Some of the Django Darisset Blog CMS functionality are:

1. Different virtual environments for development, testing and production
2. Internationalization and localization to support multiple languages
3. Project structure
4. HTML5 Boiler Plate
5. Legacy templates
6. robots.txt and human.txt can be configured
7. Organized sitemap.txt
8. SEO
9. Responsive web design
10. already using Boostrap 4
11. Embed youtube
and much more

In addition, you can learn how to create this CMS concept step by step manually due to structured code writing.
